Package com.HealthBytes.executable

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Game
    The main Game class for Cyber Case.
    HighScores
    The leader boards of the game.
    LevelOne
    The LevelOne class extends LevelParent and is the first level in a series of three.
    LevelParent
    The LevelParent class is the parent to all 3 levels of the game.
    LevelThree
    The LevelThree class extends LevelParent and is the third level in a series of three.
    LevelTwo
    The LevelTwo class extends LevelParent and is the second level in a series of three.
    MainMenu
    The MainMenu class presents the user with four options to progress in the program.
    MenuParent
    The parent for all menu panels for the program.
    Quiz
    The creates a quiz panel with working buttons and questions.
    Results
    The Results class displays the score of the user's playthrough based on a number of factors collected over the levels.
    Rules
    The Rules class displays the rules of the game.
    Setup
    The Setup class prompts the user to enter a name input and verifies the highscore.txt file is accessible.
    SplashScreen
    The SplashScreen class creates a screen to introduce the user to the program.
